---

## 1. Definitions

**"Author"** : The author of the Work.

**"Work"** : the Work includes:
- Chinese (original) text content written by the Author and released on GitHub by the Author
- English (translation) text content written by the Author and released on GitHub by the Author

**"Activation Date"** : 2026-04-14 Beijing Time (UTC+8).

**"Before Activation"** : Any time strictly before the Activation Date.

**"After Activation"** : The Activation Date and all times after.

**"Adaptation"** : Any work based on the Work, including translated/derivative text work, AI-generated videos/animations/webcomics, and human art.

**"Licensee"** or **"You"**: Any individual, organization, or legal entity exercising rights under this license. Where an AI model, AI agent, or automated process generates output based on the Work, the **operator, developer, or deployer** of that AI system is the "Licensee" responsible for compliance.

**"Personal Likeness"** : A person's face, voice, or **distinctive, identifiable physical characteristics** (including but not limited to unique eye shape/color, vocal timbre, etc) that would cause a reasonable viewer or listener to identify a specific individual, whether living or deceased, even if the full face is obscured or stylized.

